This game of Othello (or Reversi) is a 1 player only version with a computer AI opponent.
The human player plays black, and goes first, while the computer AI opponent is white and goes second.
The game is written completely in Prolog.

****************
To run the game:
****************

1) Start prolog (ex. swipl)
2) Load file with: ['othello.pl'].       --(The ending period is important)
3) Start game with: run.                 --(Again, ending period needed)
